<TITLE> Joy delighted </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Nov 19 (bdnews24.com)Prime minister Sheikh Hasina's only son Sajib Wajed Joy was delighted to hear the verdict on the trial of the murder of his grandfather, 'Bangabandhu' Sheikh Mujibur Rahman. "Definitely we are happy. We got justice after so many years. We had to wait for long 34 years for this," Joy told bdnews24.com over telephone at 9:15pm Bangladesh time, "We had to struggle a lot for this final verdict of the brutal killings, said Joy, who lives in the United States . Joy also expressed his gratitude to the people of Bangladesh. bdn
